OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1780391237
OL,3,CMan who murdered student with Sikh
OL,4,Cceremonial knife jailed for life
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for life for
OL,7,Fmurdering an 18-year-old University of
OL,8,FSouthampton student with a Sikh
OL,9,Fceremonial knife.
OL,11,FVickrum Digwa, 23, stabbed finance
OL,12,Fstudent Henry Nowak five times with a
OL,13,F21cm blade that he said he carried as
OL,14,Fpart of his Sikh faith.
OL,16,FIt happened on Belmont Road,
OL,17,FSouthampton, on December 3, 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
