OL,3,CMan who murdered student with Sikh
OL,4,Cceremonial knife jailed for life
OL,6,FShe described him as "funny, handsome,
OL,7,Fprecious and kind", and added: "My
OL,8,Fbrother should not be forever 18, he
OL,9,Fdeserved to grow old and start a
OL,10,Ffamily of his own, to be an uncle to
OL,11,Fmy children."
